data.enText: a person whose job is to receive and pay out money in a bank
a machine that pays out money automatically
a person whose job is to count votes, especially in a parliament

data.chText: 说…的人；叙述者；讲故事的人；说书人
data.enText: a person who tells stories, etc.

tr: an employee of a bank who receives and pays out money
an official appointed to count the votes (especially in legislative assembly)

value.def: A teller is someone who works in a bank and who customers pay money to or get money from.

example.ex: Every bank pays close attention to the speed and accuracy of its tellers.
example.tran: 各家银行都非常注重出纳员工作的速度和准确性。
